<p><a name="As_editor" id="As_editor"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Simon_Critchley&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: As editor">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">As editor</span></h3>
<p>Critchley has edited the following book series:</p>
<ul>
<li><i>Thinking the Political</i> (Routledge)</li>
<li><i>Blackwell Readings in Continental Philosophy</i> (Blackwell)</li>
<li><i>Thinking in Action</i> (Routledge)</li>
<li><i>How to Read...</i> (Granta, London, and W.W. Norton, New York)</li>
